claude-memory-backup-*.zip

# Per-TARGET rigs — stand setup, session minting, source-derived answer keys for a specific
# application under test. Kept OUT of git deliberately: the tool must carry no trace of any one
# customer's app, and a target-shaped script in the repo is how a general tool quietly becomes a
# tool for one site. The generic half lives in lib/ (e.g. lib/recon/ground-truth.mjs, which scores
# against ANY answer key); only the rig that produces one target's key belongs here.
targets/
